@end example

@end ifnottex

The function @code{svd} normally returns only the vector of singular values.
When called with three return values, it computes
@tex
$U$, $S$, and $V$.
@end tex
@ifnottex
@var{U}, @var{S}, and @var{V}.
@end ifnottex
For example,

@example
